    "en": {
      "title": "Why does taxing casinos hurt arteries?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party General Secretary Palitha Range Bandara said why Minister Dhammika Perera has silver when Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe is going to take steps to collect taxes from non-tax paying casino and gambling businessmen.",
        "Mr. Range Bandara said that since Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe, as the Finance Minister, presented a cabinet paper last Monday to update the Casino and Gambling Ordinance to combat the racket carried by casino and gambling businessmen by evading government taxes, Mr. Range Bandara said.",
        "Mr. Range Bandara asked Mr. Dhammika Perera what is the basis for asking Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe to step down from the position of Finance Minister, less than a week after he was sworn in as the Minister.",
        "The UNP General Secretary mentioned this in a special statement to the media."
      ],
